<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>You've been invited to join a room</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .role-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-left: 8px;
    }
    .role-owner {
      background-color: #f0ad4e;
      color: white;
    }
    .role-editor {
      background-color: #5bc0de;
      color: white;
    }
    .role-viewer {
      background-color: #5cb85c;
      color: white;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>You've Been Invited!</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello,</p>
    
    <p><strong><%= inviterName %></strong> has invited you to join the room <strong><%= roomName %></strong> as a 
      <span class="role-badge role-<%= role.toLowerCase() %>"><%= role %></span>.</p>
    
    <p>Click the button below to accept the invitation and join the room. This invitation will expire in <strong><%= expiresInHours %> hours</strong>.</p>
    
    <p style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="<%= acceptUrl %>" class="button">Accept Invitation</a>
    </p>
    
    <p>If the button doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
    <p><a href="<%= acceptUrl %>" style="word-break: break-all;"><%= acceptUrl %></a></p>
    
    <p>If you don't want to join this room, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>This is an automated message from <%= appName %>. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
